The Iowa Democrats Jefferson Jackson dinner Saturday night will feature three candidates for president. Hillary Clinton, Martin O'Malley and Bernie Sanders are all set to appear at the event in Des Moines. 
Find complete coverage afterward at DesMoinesRegister.com/JJDinner and in the Des Moines Sunday Register. SPEECHES DURING THE DINNER: Black man at Carson event defends rebel flag VIDEOS : Presidential hopeful, Bernie Sanders held a rally with supporters before holding a march to the Iowa Democratic Party’s Jefferson Jackson Dinner on Saturday, Oct. 24, 2015. Kelsey Kremer/The Register Democratic presidential candidate Hillary Clinton held a rally with husband Bill and Katy Perry before the Iowa Democratic Party's annual Jefferson-Jackson Dinner in Downtown Des Moines on Saturday.
